WorkItem.Description:
When adding a font style to a ListItem in addListItem-method it is getting ignored. This is due to passing an unknown parameter to the constructor of the ListItem (the parameter is called $styleFont but $styleText is passed).

I suggest to change line 183 of Section.php:

$listItem = new PHPWord_Section_ListItem($text, $depth, $styleText, $styleList, $styleParagraph);

to

$listItem = new PHPWord_Section_ListItem($text, $depth, $styleFont, $styleList, $styleParagraph);
